      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok i get the dancer thing. but it still feels kinda like magic or something. is there any way to describe the \"spookiness\" without using metaphors like dancers or twins? like, what is actually happening in the math or the physical reality that makes it so unintuitive?",
      "source": "evaluator"
